<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />How long, all of you, will you attack a man,</para>

<para style="q1">that you may tip him over</para>

<para style="q1">like a leaning wall or a shaky fence?</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />They consult with him only to bring him down from his honorable position;</para>

<para style="q1">they love to tell lies;</para>

<para style="q1">they bless him with their mouths, but in their hearts they curse him.

<char style="qs">Selah</char></para>
